		<title>AWS AI revenue hits US$15 billion. Andy Jassy says the hard part is keeping up with demand</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/aws-ai-revenue-hits-us15-billion-andy-jassy-says-the-hard-part-is-keeping-up-with-demand/</link>
		
