					<description><![CDATA[<p>AI-powered Customer Data Cloud, Amperity, has announced an expansion of its Australian operations, including the availability of its platform in the AWS Asia-Pacific Sydney and Melbourne Regions, after growing demand from enterprises that require local data residency and scale. Amperity&#8217;s footprint in Australia has doubled in size over the past year, having gained customers including [&#8230;]</p>
